WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.100
Mom.

2
00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:03.933
How dare you fight with my grandson over soup?

3
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:04.866
Return the bowl.

4
00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:06.100
I’ll show you what happens

5
00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:07.400
if you try to take it again.

6
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:08.966
Stop!

7
00:00:13.566 --> 00:00:14.333
Let me see.

8
00:00:15.266 --> 00:00:15.833
Don’t be afraid,

9
00:00:16.133 --> 00:00:16.766
Mom’s here.

10
00:00:17.233 --> 00:00:18.066
What’s going on now?

11
00:00:18.266 --> 00:00:19.333
You people are too much.

12
00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:20.766
Bullying a child too?

13
00:00:20.933 --> 00:00:21.600
Li Bei Qīng,

14
00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:23.333
this is the Zhang family.

15
00:00:23.666 --> 00:00:25.100
You have no place here.

16
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:25.933
The Zhang family?

17
00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:27.766
I wonder after tonight

18
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:28.933
if there will still be a Zhang family?

19
00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:30.933
What do you mean?

20
00:00:31.066 --> 00:00:32.100
Why don’t you make a call and find out?

21
00:00:32.833 --> 00:00:34.533
Now there’s not a single cent in your account,

22
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:36.200
and all your assets

23
00:00:36.266 --> 00:00:37.500
have been seized.

24
00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:38.166
You,

25
00:00:38.433 --> 00:00:39.366
are bankrupt.

26
00:00:41.433 --> 00:00:42.333
Zhang Wen Xu,

27
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:44.066
you illegally kidnapped a child

28
00:00:44.066 --> 00:00:45.266
and engaged in malicious bidding.

29
00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:47.200
The police are on their way.

30
00:00:51.766 --> 00:00:52.600
Impossible.

31
00:00:53.066 --> 00:00:54.833
You two are working together to trick me, right?

32
00:00:54.933 --> 00:00:56.200
You think I’ll believe it?

33
00:00:58.300 --> 00:00:59.233
Want to answer the call?

34
00:01:02.966 --> 00:01:03.700
President Zhang,

35
00:01:04.033 --> 00:01:05.833
the police just came and seized Jian An Group.

36
00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:07.100
We’re bankrupt.

37
00:01:07.833 --> 00:01:08.633
No way, no way.

38
00:01:08.633 --> 00:01:09.266
Impossible.

39
00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:11.266
Absolutely not.

40
00:01:11.266 --> 00:01:12.500
You did this, didn’t you?

41
00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:14.133
Don’t move.
